~ breath
Beatrice the Bee: deeeeeeep.....breathhhhh....
- *take a deep breath* 
	=> breath_done
- OK => END
=> END

~ breath_done
Beatrice the Bee: That's the spririt! Go for a walk, it'll do ya some good. I'll wait over there. 
do reward_bee()
=> END

~ default
Beatrice the Bee: Go for a walk, it'll do ya some good. 
Beatrice the Bee: You can press "q" to return here at any time.
Beatrice the Bee: There's a jukebox if the solitary sound of your breath feels too oppressive. 
=> END

~ bee_sunflower
